---
description: Build, lint, and test verification before commits
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Before suggesting any commit:
1. Run `npm run lint` from the root to verify ESLint passes
2. Run `npm run test` from the root to execute the Vitest suite with coverage
3. Run `npm run build` from the root to verify the Angular build passes
4. Do not suggest bypassing `.husky/pre-commit` (lint-staged) or `.husky/commit-msg` (commitlint)
5. If any step fails, fix the issue before proceeding to commit
